us.conxio.HL7.HL7MessageService
Class HL7Route

java.lang.Object
  us.conxio.HL7.HL7MessageService.HL7SpecificationElement
      us.conxio.HL7.HL7MessageService.HL7Route

public class HL7Route
extends HL7SpecificationElement

An object encapsulating the inbound source, outbound destination, qualification and exclusion filtering, and transformations for a given HL7 transaction vector.

IsQualified

public boolean IsQualified(HL7Message msg)
Determines whether or not argument HL7Message qualifies for passage according to the context HL7Specification.

Parameters:
msg - a HL7Message which is tested against the qualifications of the context HL7Specification.
Returns:
true if the argument HL7Message qualifies for passage, by any HL7Transform, or false if it does not. Note that the message will not qualify if the route contains no HL7Transforms
